Interface RegistrationApprovalService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegistrationApprovalServiceImpl

    public interface RegistrationApprovalService
    RegistrationApprovalService is the interface for registration approval service. This class fetches the Registration Packets pending for approval and for updating the status of Registration packets
